data.description: This property has a well designed traditional floor-plan offering space for a variety of needs! You enter into generous sized living & dining rooms with soaring vaulted ceiling. Kitchen island with additional seating, granite, stainless steel appliances, gas fireplace in casual family room with built-ins. Bedroom & full bath on the main level is ideal for guests who don't want to use stairs. The primary suite offers large walk-in, double vanity sinks and nice size vanity. The large loft area adds to the versatility of this design. Recent updates include NEW carpet throughout and NEW paint. This home has central A/C and includes the washer/dryer. The lot has a fully fenced backyard with covered patio, garden beds and sprinkler system. Copperleaf neighborhood is aligned to good schools and close proximity to Intel, Nike, shopping, dining, bus-line and recreational park. Come take a look at this great value! Open House Sat 10/14 & Sun 10/15 from 1:30pm - 3:30pm.
